---
import Layout from "../../components/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Home-lab">
  <section class="project-section">
    <h1>Home-lab</h1>
    <img src="/project_photos/dataserver.png" alt="Photo of laptop" class="large-project-image" />
    <div class="project-description">
      <p>
        I repurposed an old HP EliteBook as a dedicated <strong>Ubuntu Server</strong>, turning it into the core of my home-lab.  
        The server runs <strong>Apache</strong> for web hosting and <strong>Nextcloud</strong> with a <strong>MariaDB</strong> backend, providing a secure private cloud solution for storing and syncing files (photos, documents, media) across my devices.  
        I also configured <strong>custom subdomains</strong> with HTTPS using Let's Encrypt, allowing me to self-host tools and web apps accessible from anywhere.  
        This project gave me hands-on experience with server administration, networking, SSL certificates, and cloud storage infrastructure.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>


<style>
  .project-section {
    padding: 4rem 1rem;
    background-color: #1e1e24;
    color: #f1f1f1;
    text-align: center;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: #5DD5FF;
  }

  p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #c4c4c4;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .large-project-image {
    width: 100%; 
    height: auto;
    max-width: 400px;
    border-radius: 8px; 
    margin-bottom: 2rem; 
  }

  .project-description {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .project-links {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 2rem; /* Space between the logos */
  }

  .logo-link {
    width: 80px; /* Adjust the logo size */
    height: auto;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .logo-link:hover {
    filter: opacity(0.8) drop-shadow(0 0 10px #5DD5FF);
    transform: scale(1.1); /* Scale up the logo on hover */
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .large-project-image {
      max-width: 100%; /* Allow the image to be responsive */
    }

    .project-section {
      padding: 2rem 1rem; /* Adjust padding for smaller screens */
    }
  }
</style>
